{"image_id": "NFLX_2009_page_80", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "NETFLIX, INC.", "bbox": [545.8, 140.2, 692.1, 161.0]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS—(Continued)", "bbox": [279.5, 177.7, 958.7, 198.5]}, {"text": "9.", "bbox": [143.8, 227.7, 159.4, 248.6]}, {"text": "Employee Benefit Plan", "bbox": [180.3, 227.7, 383.1, 248.6]}, {"text": "The Company maintains a 401(k) savings plan covering substantially all of its employees. Eligible", "bbox": [185.5, 265.4, 1094.0, 286.3]}, {"text": "employees may contribute up to 60% of their annual salary through payroll deductions, but not more than the", "bbox": [143.8, 290.4, 1094.1, 311.3]}, {"text": "statutory limits set by the Internal Revenue Service. The Company matches employee contributions at the", "bbox": [143.8, 315.4, 1094.1, 336.3]}, {"text": "discretion of the Board of Directors. During 2009, 2008 and 2007, the Company’s matching contributions totaled", "bbox": [143.8, 340.5, 1094.0, 361.3]}, {"text": "$2.3 million, $2.0 million and $1.5 million, respectively.", "bbox": [143.8, 365.5, 617.5, 386.3]}, {"text": "10.", "bbox": [143.8, 427.8, 169.9, 448.6]}, {"text": "Related Party Transaction", "bbox": [190.7, 427.8, 427.0, 448.6]}, {"text": "In April 2007, Netflix entered into a license agreement with a company in which an employee had a", "bbox": [185.5, 465.5, 1094.2, 486.3]}, {"text": "significant ownership interest at that time. Pursuant to this agreement, Netflix recorded a charge of $2.5 million", "bbox": [143.8, 490.5, 1094.0, 511.3]}, {"text": "in technology and development expense. In January 2008, in conjunction with various arrangements Netflix paid", "bbox": [143.8, 515.5, 1094.1, 536.4]}, {"text": "a total of $6.0 million to this same company, of which $5.7 million was accounted for as an investment under the", "bbox": [143.8, 540.5, 1094.1, 561.4]}, {"text": "cost method. In conjunction with these arrangements, the employee with the significant ownership interest in the", "bbox": [143.8, 565.5, 1094.1, 586.4]}, {"text": "same company terminated his employment with Netflix. In the fourth quarter of 2009, Netflix sold its investment", "bbox": [143.8, 590.5, 1094.0, 611.4]}, {"text": "in this company to an unrelated party and realized a pre-tax gain of $1.8 million.", "bbox": [143.8, 615.5, 816.4, 636.4]}, {"text": "11.", "bbox": [143.8, 677.9, 169.9, 698.7]}, {"text": "Selected Quarterly Financial Data (Unaudited)", "bbox": [190.7, 677.9, 607.9, 698.7]}, {"text": "December 31", "bbox": [684.7, 722.8, 777.7, 739.4]}, {"text": "September 30", "bbox": [798.6, 722.8, 896.2, 739.4]}, {"text": "June 30", "bbox": [928.5, 722.8, 983.6, 739.4]}, {"text": "March 31", "bbox": [1020.6, 722.8, 1089.6, 739.4]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [143.8, 752.9, 185.5, 773.7]}, {"text": "Total revenues . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [143.8, 778.1, 663.8, 798.9]}, {"text": "$444,542", "bbox": [692.2, 778.1, 770.3, 798.9]}, {"text": "423,120", "bbox": [818.8, 778.1, 886.5, 798.9]}, {"text": "408,509", "bbox": [927.5, 778.1, 995.2, 798.9]}, {"text": "394,098", "bbox": [1026.5, 778.1, 1094.2, 798.9]}, {"text": "Gross profit . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [143.8, 803.1, 663.8, 823.9]}, {"text": "169,056", "bbox": [702.6, 803.1, 770.3, 823.9]}, {"text": "147,846", "bbox": [818.8, 803.1, 886.5, 823.9]}, {"text": "139,266", "bbox": [927.5, 803.1, 995.2, 823.9]}, {"text": "134,830", "bbox": [1026.5, 803.1, 1094.2, 823.9]}, {"text": "Net income . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [143.8, 828.1, 663.8, 848.9]}, {"text": "30,913", "bbox": [713.0, 828.1, 770.3, 848.9]}, {"text": "30,141", "bbox": [829.2, 828.1, 886.5, 848.9]}, {"text": "32,443", "bbox": [937.9, 828.1, 995.2, 848.9]}, {"text": "22,363", "bbox": [1036.9, 828.1, 1094.2, 848.9]}, {"text": "Net income per share:", "bbox": [143.8, 853.1, 32